@startuml

title 离线优先决策流程（MCP 自动路由 + installer 本地命中）

start
:接收安装请求(product);
:pm_probe_network(product);

if (recommended_mode == online?) then (yes)
  :进入远端在线安装;
  :pm_skill_install_guarded;
  stop
else (no)
  :进入离线分支;
  :pm_offline_manifest;
  :本地执行离线投放脚本\n下载 package + signature 并上传远端;
  :pm_check_offline_artifacts;
  if (ready_for_offline_install?) then (yes)
    :pm_skill_install_guarded;
    stop
  else (no)
    :返回 artifact_not_ready 错误;
    stop
  endif
endif

note right
  installer 内部仍保留离线优先逻辑：
  ensure_local_or_download(destination)
  - destination 文件存在且非空 -> 直接复用
  - 不存在 -> 尝试在线下载
  - 下载失败 -> 返回 Offline install hint
end note

@enduml
